    "method": "Canonical Bailey & L\u00f3pez de Prado. SR0 = mean_SR + std_SR * E[max_N] with E[max_N] from exact inverse-normal quantiles (1-\u03b3)\u03a6\u207b\u00b9(1-1/N)+\u03b3\u03a6\u207b\u00b9(1-1/(N\u00b7e)); the selected (winner) Sharpe is deflated using the Sharpe-estimator SE sqrt((1-\u03b33\u00b7SR+(\u03b34-1)/4\u00b7SR\u00b2)/(T-1)) on the winner's in-market returns."
